answer.text:
If one object wraps (creates) another object inheriting from the `IDisposable` class, it must implement the `IDisposable` interface, as in the example below:

```
class UsingIDisposable: IDisposable
{
   private Stream m_Stream;
   //
   // ...
   //
}
```

